comments: Aldridge (SAS) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) is already in White's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Prior to the start of the upward shooting motion Forbes (SAS) reaches in and makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm on the perimeter.
Hood (POR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends DeRozan's (SAS) drive to the basket.
Tolliver (POR) is already in White's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Aldridge (SAS) is already in Lillard's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Lillard (POR) does not make contact to White's (SAS) arm as he defends the shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.

McCollum (POR) briefly places his hand to Aldridge's (SAS) side but immediately removes his hands and he does not extend his hands into Aldridge.  The contact is marginal and does not affect Aldridge's ability to secure the rebound.
White (SAS) legally contests Lillard's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) places his hand momentarily on Mills' (SAS) side before correcting.
Mills (SAS) is already in Hood's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
DeRozan (SAS) extends his arm as he releases from the contact with Hood (POR) and does not affect Hood's ability to defend.
Lillard (POR) extends his arm as he releases from the contact with White (SAS), and the contact does not affect White's ability to defend.
Mills (SAS) engages with Simons (POR) but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
DeRozan (SAS) makes contact with the ball during the rebound and the contact to McCollum's (POR) body is considered incidental.
DeRozan (SAS) breaks the plane of the free throw line prior to the ball making contact with the rim.
Forbes (SAS) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Lyles (SAS) loses control of the ball on his own prior to the incidental body contact by Tolliver (POR).
White (SAS) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
